des:
Use the C. N. G. Stations alexa skill to find C.N.G. Fueling stations in your zip code around the U.S. Simply enable the skill and say "Alexa, open C. N. G. Stations" to begin. 

Or say "Alexa, ask C. N. G. Stations..."
• get me zip code 90012 
• Is there Fueling station around 90012

This is a beta version which only holds information on basic C.N.G. Fueling Stations for now. Stay tuned, more features will be added soon!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
